{"tid":1490870,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"如此美麗無私的香港人 - 林夕","createTime":"2019-08-20T08:29:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T18:21:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d0fa0afc15f0bde0bfb757fd6887d8def8d4eb0f","tid":1490870,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:29:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9E%97%E5%A4%95/daily/article/20190820/20751951\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E5%25A4%2595%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190820%2F20751951&d=QZ1X7Ww%2BB3pe%2FYPW%2Fe6VuZMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=156c6b03\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E5%25A4%2595%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190820%2F20751951&h=d29bf29d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9E%97%E5%A4%95/daily/article/20190820/20751951</a><br />\n<br />\n如此美麗無私的香港人 - 林夕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190820/large/1566206576_525b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190820%2Flarge%2F1566206576_525b.jpg&h=a6f59925&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n說航拍下的雨傘森林開滿整個港島，漂亮到震撼國際，其實有點不仁。<br />\n<br />\n這美麗畫面背後，有多少汗水淚水血水，兩個多月以至二十年有多的怨氣累積堆疊而成。<br />\n<br />\n大陸封鎖真相、顛倒是非、栽贓嫁禍，口口聲聲一小撮暴徒鬧事。如果這樣的畫面外銷轉內銷，如此多暴徒冒雨舉傘，如此擁擠緩慢而沒發生任何衝突，這樣的暴徒也未免太斯文了。<br />\n<br />\n有些香港人依然信不過香港人，仍然真心覺得有人收錢、有人受媒體教唆、有人受外國勢力支配，一百七十多萬人，你叫神盾局策劃一次這樣進退有序的逛街行動給世人看看。除非你是環球時報胡錫進，會把這次和平而堅定的遊行，歸功於深圳軍演的恫嚇，引發「暴力退潮」。如果鬧事者有那麼聽話，會被嚇怕，就不是暴徒了。<br />\n<br />\n香港人真的很有心，很有耐心，很細心。和你飛超出了一點紅線之後，此刻需要一個和理非的行動，就和理非給你看，須要多少默契，心靈要有多相同才能做到啊。這次不是一組幾百人的游擊戰與警隊對壘，組員之間看形勢變化而行事。這次是百多萬人，從維園第一批走出維園之後，民陣就不能控制大局，但是大局在大家心中。<br />\n<br />\n某些人堵人堵了很久的地帶，後面的人喊開路，前面的人發現是巴士被人群堵住，隨即重演分紅海，巴士去後，人流隨即通暢，繼續向前推進。少一點遊行經驗以及默契，就會互相吵起來亂起來，難度之高，出埃及記也不外如此。碰到了紅衣人，明知也不必故問了，就是不被你挑釁不再中你計，不再讓你成為英雄，幽默不止能救世，也能四両撥千斤；中央那麼喜歡屈港人以港獨，也倒過來跟紅衣人合照，祝他一句福建獨立，嚇跑他比拳頭更有效。<br />\n<br />\n警方在命根寶貝中聯辦附近嚴陣以待，講明和理非，大部分人就不讓你得逞，到中聯辦前就行人止步，大海無量，卻要退就退。<br />\n<br />\n剩下來無事可做，警察只能截查市民，不知是否不甘心，抑或有疑心症，竟然問身穿黃色反光衣的急救員：「把鉸剪用嚟做咩？」救護員有剪刀，正如教車師傅有士巴拿，合情合理，如果那救護員回警察說是用來割席的，不知道會不會被控以阻差辦公？<br />\n<br />\n如此美麗聰明靈活無私的香港人，是如何煉成的？很可惜，是一場漫長的災難裏一點一滴撿拾到的。林鄭不配有這樣的市民，竟以為派錢可以拖延可以打散士氣，那就好好繼續聽行政會議的意見，查一查神盾局的地址，收拾亂局吧。 <br />\n<br />\n林夕<br />\n電郵 :linxiapple@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n中國人民生活現實 (左丁山)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n童 言 (李碧華)"},{"pid":"2467a31f6d48ff26adc9812365dcca2b160e0a8e","tid":1490870,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:30:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7aca51c428cb6f1cfd85d2224a1589d1a779f53","tid":1490870,"uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:34:21.000Z","msg":"好靚呀， 香港人真係好美麗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5aVhYVp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5aVhYVp.jpg&h=78e611a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n親眼睇住由無落雨到落雨, 睇住佢哋開遮.<br />\n<br />\n無一個人走, 企定定係到等入維園.<br />\n<br />\n睇住佢哋唔郁差不多成兩個鐘.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2404a8c96e11d359560d94b187cd8d758aa3b44f","tid":1490870,"uid":9570,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:34:43.000Z","msg":"香港人質素放諸世界首屈一指<br />\n<br />\n就算只比一片爛地都可以活出價值，哪裡有香港人，哪裡就是香港"},{"pid":"09ebdbd0a05bedc776f3f15443392e957f1869cb","tid":1490870,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:35:09.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港自由之書&mdash;賣卡投資國難五金發國難財Ver 2.0</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1486618/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1486618/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"79636c5fa1aab88b7f82ec5b75ea91080642d454","tid":1490870,"uid":57044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:35:32.000Z","msg":"夕爺"},{"pid":"a85ae71958bdadcc11f865ab7670b1c58ba70243","tid":1490870,"uid":102609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:35:50.000Z","msg":"夕爺完全唔驚俾人封殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffed11b167443522480fb64701c7ab1ea95e96a2","tid":1490870,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:36:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3903c6fa74f4cf6b9226cc3ba901d21be8ab16d","tid":1490870,"uid":91192,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"a85ae71958bdadcc11f865ab7670b1c58ba70243","tid":1490870,"uid":102609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:35:50.000Z","msg":"夕爺完全唔驚俾人封殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:38:45.000Z","msg":"你要搞清楚係夕爺俾人封殺定夕爺封殺人"},{"pid":"1d28f26ea2d4bced210a9095c6482afaf6ea8a0a","tid":1490870,"uid":310534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0