n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GNnktPY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGNnktPY.png&h=3e335eff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oyCktPZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoyCktPZ.png&h=b2150e93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vJVeygF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvJVeygF.png&h=9235ff7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cb38145db6a63450d635f5b5e5f700134309ec32","tid":1490870,"uid":72301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:43:17.000Z","msg":"大海無量，卻要退就退。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明就係be water <br />\n但唔知係咪知道出自佢支筆嘅心理作用<br />\n成個意境出曬黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c86c568ad6a99ffad89231dc4655f446f89668e0","tid":1490870,"uid":77220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T09:43:20.000Z","msg":"夕爺"},{"pid":"f615e0f30e9cf2e85b698a6e0fc565615e2cd901","tid":1490870,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T14:26:58.000Z","msg":"唔落呢場雨 都感覺唔到啲人個心係咁 firm.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca633b019a7804e3f98be88d877775c87b1cc2dc","tid":1490870,"uid":244315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T14:30:26.000Z","msg":"夕爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f345624f57f10a94c868d35d453c617039e9ca2","t